info: Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2023,  · Stayed one night
Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2023,  · Stayed over a week

rating_comment:
The rate listed on Airbnb (probably, by the apartment owner or Airbnb) was much higher than direct booking at the place/Maati Properties and other accommodation booking apps/websites. Toilet at the check-in area is unclean, unfinished, and the commode top was broken which can injure people.
Owner didn't provide mat outside toilet, toilet tissue Paper etc. No microwave and restaurant doesn't provide tea before 12pm. Coffee isn't available there at all. Only 1 plate and 1 glass for 2 guests. I wasn't given the apartment I booked. Please avoid 201 (250Sft is too small to be called a studio apartment) or anything on the first (no level 1, G and then, 2,3...) floor and possibly, 2nd floor as too much noises and even, people talking could be heard from the room. Overall, customer service was very poor. However, this is a great and fantastic place (close from airport and very convenient location) to stay if basic/minor changes are made and staffs are trained properly in customer service.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · August 2022,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment: Outstanding environment and lovely place to stay. The room was clean and i had very peaceful 11 days of experience. No disturbance or issues at all. Everything in the room is handy. Thanks to all the hosts, they have been super friendly and supportive. Especially host "Keya", she is doing a marvellous job. Keep up the good work, hope to see you soon again.

info: Rating, 1 star,  · August 2022,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: To solve an issue she came with ideas including more issues.

the place was a bit untidy when compared to hotels at same price. the AC is subpar although functional. and I had asked for plates in the room at the reception I didn't get them. and while leaving the reception desk asked me to stay until the room is checked. after the check, I was kind of accused of stealing the AC remote. I had to go into the room again after checkout to show them that the AC remote which was in plain sight. it's better to stay at a hotel than here.
